Download-URL: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/geotools/
Description: **geotools** is a small collection of geometrical classes
        and functions accessable from both Python and Cython.
        
         * Point, Vector & Planes
         * Bounding box
         * Transformations
         * A camera class
        
